data.name: Spinach Salad with Berries
data.quickTastyDescription: A refreshing and vibrant salad featuring fresh spinach topped with sweet berries and a light dressing.
detailedCookingInstructions: Wash the fresh spinach thoroughly and pat dry.
In a large bowl, add the spinach and top with mixed berries.
Sprinkle crumbled feta cheese and chopped walnuts on top.
Drizzle balsamic vinaigrette over the salad just before serving.
Toss gently to combine all ingredients.
data.detailedName: Fresh Spinach Salad with Berries, Feta, and Walnuts
